@startuml zero_trust_journey
title Zero Trust Maturity Journey
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #f0f9ff

start
:Stage 1 — Traditional Perimeter\n(VPN, on-prem AD);
:Stage 2 — Identity-Aware Proxy\n(EntraID, Conditional Access);
:Stage 3 — Device Trust\n(Intune MDM, Compliance Policies);
:Stage 4 — Micro-Segmentation\n(UIAO Addressing Plane);
:Stage 5 — Full UIAO Overlay\n(Policy Orchestrator + Telemetry);
:Stage 6 — FedRAMP ATO\n(Continuous Monitoring);
stop
@enduml
